# >>>>> PUBG PC (Steam 绝地求生) 分流规则 <<<<<

# ====== 游戏主程序与官方大厅 ======
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,pubg
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,tslgame
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,playbattlegrounds.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pubg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,battlegroundsgame.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chunk.live.playbattlegrounds.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,intlgame.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,levelinfinite.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gameloop.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,idtopup.com

# ====== 核心域名后缀 (DOMAIN-SUFFIX) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pubgmobile.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gpubgm.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,levelinfinite.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,intlgame.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,proximabeta.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,amsoveasea.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,igamecj.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vnggames.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pax.ucloudgda.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wellbia.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,acesecure.net

# ====== 核心反作弊系统 (关键：不走代理极易卡死或报初始化错误) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,battleye.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wellbia.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xigncode.info
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cloud.vnggames.vn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tgpa.qq.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,wellbia
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,acesecure

# ====== 额外补充：Steam 平台登录与社区 (可选，若已在 Game.list 中可不加) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,steampowered.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,steamstatic.com

# ====== 游戏内语音系统 (偶尔卡在进局时，因为语音被拦截) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gcloud.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,itopstory.com

# ====== 腾讯海外云及对局服务器常用 IP 段 (IP-CIDR) ======
# 加上 no-resolve 是为了让代理软件不强制在本地解析它，直接交由节点处理，防止高延迟
IP-CIDR,162.62.0.0/16,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,119.28.0.0/16,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,150.109.0.0/16,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,43.129.0.0/16,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,129.226.0.0/16,no-resolve
